The paper deals with the problem of storing prefix codes efficiently, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also introduces several techniques for storing prefix codes, which is a topic related to algorithms and complexity (cs.DC). The experimental comparison of the techniques involves measuring the time and space complexity, which is a topic related to systems and control (cs.SI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
